      <div class="col-md-7">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">What do we do? <span class="text-muted">Help you find the documents you need.</span></h2>
        <p class="lead">Provide a platform where students and other professionals can quickly mine the data from a list of PDF files acquired.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <img src="/assets/icon-what-we-do.png" id="featuretteimages">
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

