        <p class="lead">We are PDRank, a group of developers that strive to find the latest and most effective treatments for patients
          with a certain set of conditions, no longer requiring the most experienced doctors to have to continuously read papers
          to stay up to date.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <img src="/assets/whoarewe.png" id="featuretteimages">
